  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and saut\u0017 until fragrant.",
    "Add the Chinese long beans and cook until slightly tender.",
    "Add the ferment kimchi, turmeric, cayenne pepper, soy sauce, honey, water, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Cover the pot and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Transfer the pot to the preheated oven and braise for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and garnish with fresh cilantro."
